EGRET

library(EGRET)
# Sample data included in package:
eList <- Choptank_eList
# Multi-line plots:
date1 <- "2000-09-01"
date2 <- "2005-09-01"
date3 <- "2009-09-01"
qBottom<-100
qTop<-5000
clevel<-seq(0,2,0.5)
maxDiff<-0.8
yearStart <- 2000
yearEnd <- 2010
fluxBiasMulti(eList)

plotContours(eList, yearStart,yearEnd,qBottom,qTop, 
             contourLevels = clevel,qUnit=1)

plotDiffContours(eList, yearStart,yearEnd,
                 qBottom,qTop,maxDiff,qUnit=1)
